data.description: Welcome to your new home in the highly sought-after Cedar Crest neighborhood! This delightful 3-bedroom residence offers the perfect blend of space, comfort, and style, making it a fantastic opportunity for a family looking to settle in a wonderful community. This inviting open floor plan is perfect for entertaining. Convenience is at your doorstep with this exceptional location! You'll be just moments away from schools,  shopping centers, and major highways, ensuring that your daily commute and errands are a breeze. The Roof and gutters replaced in 2021 and new carpeting has been installed upstairs.
